module.exports = add

/**
 * Adds two vec2's
 *
 * @param {vec2} out the receiving vector
 * @param {vec2} a the first operand
 * @param {vec2} b the second operand
 * @returns {vec2} out
 */
function add(out, a, b) {
    out[0] = a[0] + b[0]
    out[1] = a[1] + b[1]
    return out
}
